    dc:description "FIGURES 3 – 10. Macutula aracoiaba sp. nov. 3 – 8 left male palp, (3 ventral, 4 retrolateral, 5 dorsal, 6 prolateral, 7 anterior view, 8 clarified bulb, ventral view); 9 epigyne, ventral view; 10 vulva, dorsal view." ;
